# HR Onboarding Sync

Date: 2026-07-07
Department: People Operations
Attendees: Maya Johnson, Priya Sharma

## Issues Addressed

- New hire laptop provisioning is delayed for the August onboarding group.
- Three hires do not have application access requests approved.
- People Operations needs a workflow ticket to track provisioning status.

## Decisions

- Handle onboarding provisioning as a task because there is no active outage.
- Escalate only if devices are not shipped within two business days.

## Action Items

- Create a Jira task for August onboarding laptop and application access tracking.
- Include new hire count, required applications, and shipment deadline.

